oji\" />"},{"pid":"b13400e8597de25c914184d3c81efa5cfe6ece19","tid":27990,"uid":2175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"做樹洞好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別你覺得堆人只係搵緊個發洩位發洩 而根本唔在乎個樹洞係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}